Guardians of the Galaxy Uncovered

This "behind the scenes" show provides history of the Guardians from the comic books, character backstories, together with interviews with cast and crew and a variety of clips from the upcoming movie.

People featured in the episode include the director James Gunn, Chris Pratt (Peter Quill / Star-Lord), Zoe Saldana (Gamora), Dave Bautista (Drax), Bradley Cooper (voice of Rocket), Vin Diesel (voice of Groot)

This aired on Teletoon Canada in late July, 2014. The movie starts on Aug 1, 2014.
